title: Bug 116564 - Title of hyperlink builder changes to 'www.actuate.com' instead of 'Hyperlink Options'
OB: When clicking on 'OK' and then reopening the hyperlink builder, the actual result is that the title of the hyperlink builder changes to 'www.actuate.com'.
EB: The expected result is that the title of the hyperlink builder should be 'Hyperlink Options'.
SR:
To reproduce: 
1. Click on 'OK'.
2. Reopen the hyperlink builder.
